### AidFlow API — Users endpoints
# REST Client extension: click 'Send Request' above each block

@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000/api/v1
@token = REPLACE_WITH_JWT_TOKEN

### List users (501 in Sprint 1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get user by ID (501 in Sprint 1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/USER_ID
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get current user profile (501 in Sprint 1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update user role (501 in Sprint 1)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/USER_ID/role
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "role": "ngo_admin"
}

### Deactivate user (501 in Sprint 1)
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/USER_ID/deactivate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
